'''Ashley Wood''' (born [[1971]]) is an artist who has contributed to several ''Star Wars'' projects. He uses a blend of painting, digital photography, and graphic software, which gives his artwork a unique feel.

Ashley was born in Australia in 1971. He has worked with many major companies including [[LucasArts]], [[Lucasfilm]], DC Comics, [[Wizards of the Coast]], Paizo, [[Marvel Comics]], Activision, Dreamworks SKG, Warner Bros., Hasbro, Random House, McFarlane Entertainment, [[IDW Publishing|IDW]], and Konami. Wood is a three-time Spectrum Award winner and a two-time Communication Arts award winner.

